82
0:05:10.33,000 --> 0:05:13,000
And yeah, it's the sort of thing you produce when you're doodling on the phone.

83
0:05:13.33,000 --> 0:05:16,000
(Laughter)

84
0:05:16.33,000 --> 0:05:17,000
And this is my --

85
0:05:17.33,000 --> 0:05:2,000
(Laughter)

86
0:05:20.33,000 --> 0:05:24,000
-- you can see now the whole thing takes up far less space.

87
0:05:24.33,000 --> 0:05:27,000
