0:09:42.33,000 --> 0:09:48,000
(Laughter)

158
0:09:48.33,000 --> 0:09:51,000
And here, that's one of my favorites.

159
0:09:51.33,000 --> 0:09:54,000
Tidying up Rene Magritte -- this is really fun.

160
0:09:54.33,000 --> 0:09:55,000
You know, there is a --

